	Smoking Scarlett    
	London, July 29 (PTI): With their first marriage anniversary around the corner, Scarlett Johanssons husband Ryan Reynold has asked his actress wife to quit smoking.      
	The couple married on September 27 after dating for almost a year. Johansson is seeking treatment to quit the habit. Scarlett has sworn to her shining knight shell kick nicotine to prove shes the worlds happiest wife. Now shes researching hypnosis therapy, a source close to the actress said.                                                                                                                                                                        
